msgstr "Ajusta los parámetros que se pasan a la hoja de estilo."

#. Tag: title
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Utilización"

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most common way to run <command>meinproc6</command> is simply as "
"<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> is usually "
"index.docbook. This command creates &HTML; pages from the DocBook file. Note "
"that these pages are only viewable in &kde;-based browsers (like "
"&konqueror;)."
msgstr ""
"El modo mas habitual de ejecutar <command>meinproc6</command> es "
"sencillamente como<literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> <replaceable>docbook-file</"
"replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> donde <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable> es, "
"generalmente index.docbook. Esta orden genera páginas &HTML; a partir del "
"archivo DocBook. Estas páginas solo son visibles en navegadores basados en "
"&kde; (como &konqueror;)."

#. Tag: para
#: man-meinproc6.1.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need to view the &HTML; output in another browser (for example, if "
"you're placing it on line), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> where <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> is the "
"full path to one of the &XSL; stylesheets in &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. To "
"produce output suitable for the web, you can use <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> or <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. See the "
"<filename>README</filename> file in that directory for more details."
msgstr ""
"Si necesita ver la salida &HTML; en otro navegador (por ejemplo, si la está "
"haciendo disponible con conexión), use <literallayout>\n"
"<userinput><command>meinproc6</command> --stylesheet <replaceable>stylesheet-"
"name</replaceable> <replaceable>docbook-file</replaceable>\n"
"</userinput>\n"
"</literallayout> donde <replaceable>stylesheet-name</replaceable> es la ruta "
"completa a una de las hojas de estilo &XSL; en &lt;"
"kdoctools_installation_prefix&gt;/share/kf5/kdoctools/customization/. Para "
"generar salida adecuada para la web, puede emplear <command>kde-web.xsl</"
"command> o <command>kde-chunk-online.xsl</command>. Consulte el archivo "
"<filename>README</filename> situado en este directorio para obtener más "
"información."

